content.rendered:
Directed by Nilaanjan Reeta Datta

Written by Raaghav Dar. Nilaanjan Reeta Datta. Nilaanjan Reeta Datta. Bhushan Ingole. Rohit Kumar

Cast Anurag Sinha (Nirbhay kalita). Mishti Chakraborthy (Rimli Bora). Hemant Kher (Dr.Dhiren Kalita). Rakesh Chaturvedi Om (Police Inspector). Ranjeev lal Baruah (Bhavik). Monuj Borkotoky (Debojit). Ranjita Boruah (Puravi Kalita). Stuti Choudhury (Ratna Kalita). Bibhuti Bhushan Hazarika (News Editor). Rohit Kp (Chinmoy). Soumya Mukherjee (Rishab Banerjee). KP Sandhu (Neeraj Deka). Saharsh Kumar Shukla (kamal Sharma). Akash Sinha (Mukul). Violet Nazir Tiwari (Mother)

Language Hindi

Producers Munna Bhagat. Rassmin Bora. Nilaanjan Reeta Datta. Kiran Doke. Anil Goswami. Shitiz Jain. Rahul Kapoor. Siddharth Mahajan. Navnita Sen.

Production Finchbill Motion Pictures
